parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to become difficult or impossible to turn, making it hard to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The power steering warning light is illuminated
the steering wheel becomes stiff or locks
the vehicle is difficult to steer
the power steering assist fault message is displayed
and the vehicle may require excessive force to turn.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Airbag warning light illuminated
airbags did not deploy in a crash
airbag sensor malfunction
airbag module needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The Takata airbag recall has left many owners without a functioning airbag system, putting them at risk of serious injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Received recall notification
but parts are not available
dealer unable to perform repair
manufacturer exceeded reasonable time for recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can lead to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: Brake pedal went to the floor
vehicle failed to stop
ABS warning light illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Various issues with the vehicle can lead to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: Fuel system malfunction
front passenger seat shakes
traction warning light illuminated
seat belt malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the PTU can cause the vehicle to suddenly stop or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle shakes or vibrates
the vehicle suddenly stops or loses power
the vehicle makes a grinding noise
the vehicle acts like the brake is being engaged and disengaged.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to slip or hesitate, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle lurches or jerks
the vehicle makes a clunking noise
the vehicle has delayed or harsh shifting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the throttle body can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the vehicle hesitates or lags
the vehicle makes a burning odor
the vehicle has a wrench symbol on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the hybrid system can cause the vehicle to lose power or have reduced performance, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power or has reduced performance
the vehicle operates exclusively in gas power mode
the vehicle has jerking or hesitation when transitioning between gas and EV modes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose stopping power, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle has a sudden loss of braking power
the vehicle has a grinding noise when applying the brakes
the vehicle has a delay in braking response.
